'''Adam Smith''' ,d adamsan Abritani i yeɣra taflsuft ula ladɣa tadamsa. Ilul deg 5 yunyu 1723 di Kirkcaldy ([[Ikkus]]), d immut deg 17 yulyu 1790 deg [[Edinburg|Edinburg]] (Ikkus) asmi ɣur-es 67 iseggwasen deg laɛmer. 

Aṭas n medden ssnen Adam Smith asmi yura yiwen udlis g useggwas n  1776 umi qqaren Wealth of Nations ([[Ayla n Iɣlanen]]); d bab n weḍru n tikta n talellamt (libéralisme). 

==Ayen yura Adam Smith==

*The Theory of Moral Sentiments (1759) 
*An Inquiry into the Nature and Causes of the Wealth of Nations (1776)

